        "timestamp": "2020-06-23 09:00:05.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nRitu, I've went with a change in a way, that other installations methods shouldn't be affected, but if you want, feel free to verify it against your other deployment methods.\nI've removed CI-specific variables as they are not CI-specific and it's hard to keep them in sync with \"defaults\" and provided differing variables as host-local variables in single host deployments.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
