        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2020-06-23 09:00:46.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nAlso one more comment, Could we consider creating Frankfurt branch for multicloud? Maybe this commit could be a good base, as it would serve stable KUD base for people to use?",
